<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1452,918,1084]" pageId="12" pageNumber="217">Characterized by the rough petiole, sheathed throughout its length with the sheath persistent, the leaf blade with elongated fenestrations towards the margin, the spathe light green during development, light green and pruinose abaxially and pale pink adaxially at anthesis.</paragraph>
